  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i1.s.hjfile.cn/entry/201507/8195db0a-8377-4a55-8b97-192c535ff449.jpeg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p795209\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\tTwo UK-listed mining giants have announced plans to slash thousands of jobs. Anglo American is one. They're cutting 6,000 positions, mostly office jobs though, not exactly at the production side. Lonmin, the world's third largest <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/platinum\" target=\"_blank\">platinum</a> producer's cutting another 6,000 jobs in South Africa. Let's get analysis now from Justin Urquhart Stewart from Seven Investment Management with us from Salford. So a pretty <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/grim\" target=\"_blank\">grim</a> day for Lonmin and Anglo American.</p>\n<p>\n\tGrim news all around actually for commodity companies. We've often heard on World Business Report over the years about the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/commodity\" target=\"_blank\">commodity</a> super cycle. Well today the wheel just fell off the cycle because you can see, not just for these two companies but a lot of the other major commodity companies as well, the effect of the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/shortfall\" target=\"_blank\">shortfall</a> in commodity prices. You only have to look at the past few months. We found iron ore down 41%, copper 18%, platinum 14%. This is actually therefore meant that you've got certain companies like Lonmin effectively going into loss and also Anglo American as well. So it's a fundamental change in their business and so we've seen their fall. Their share prices fall quite dramatically. You saw Anglo American down by some 3%. As for Lonmin, that was <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/initially\" target=\"_blank\">initially</a> down 17%, but now down actually 13%. This is how share prices have halved in the past year.</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>声明：音视频均来自互联网链接，仅供学习使用。本网站自身不存储、控制、修改被链接的内容。&ldquo;沪江</span><a>英语</a><span>&rdquo;高度重视知识产权保护。当如发现本网站发布的信息包含有侵犯其著作权的链接内容时，请联系我们，我们将依法采取措施移除相关内容或屏蔽相关链接。&gt;&gt;<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/course/52569?source=16553\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\">零基础直达流利生活口语班</a>&lt;&lt;</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p795209/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p795209\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p795700/\">每天都很累吗？做好3件小事让生活焕然一新</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p796603/\">小贝大儿子17岁的人生是这样的 看完我很受伤</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p796585/\">真正说走就走的冒险：目的地未知，你来吗？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p796128/\">教学10年的老外告诉你：美国人最常的俚语</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p796625/\">2016年iphone摄影赛获奖作品：一半来自中国</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p794753/\">6个月内你能学会的10项新技能</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p794140/\">蜜桃臀羞羞呐！日本妈咪晒萌娃PP照萌翻网友</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p796601/\">新外长鲍里斯 终于把英国政界变成了部喜剧片</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p796727/\">英语口语情景对话：请老外吃中餐</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p796272/\">10个你不知道的日常交际口语表达，超地道！</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.